description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for two enthusiastic Clinical Trial Coordinators to join the delivery team, working with the R&amp;D Delivery Manager to promote and facilitate research activity at the Trust, develop and extend the range of research undertaken and instill a Trust wide research culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent development opportunity for an organized individual, providing hands-on day to day study management to deliver increasing patient recruitment to time and target.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will be involved in the setting up and conduct of studies, data management and patient liaison. You will be required to build strong relationships with investigators, research teams, service departments and external research partners. You will be based at the Queen Elizabeth Hospital site but will be required to work cross site at Lewisham Hospital (hospital transport provided). For informal enquiries, please contact Hannah Kelly hannah.kelly@nhs.net or Allison Mascagni allison.mascagni@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameHannah KellyJob titleR &amp; D Delivery ManagerEmail addresshannah.kelly@nhs.netTelephone number0208 836 6811&lt;/p&gt;
